==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reiterative
<hw>Re*it"er*a*tive</hw> <pr>(r?-?t"?r-?-t?v)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>A word expressing repeated or
reiterated action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A word formed from another, or used to form another,
by repetition; <as>as, <ex>dillydally</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reiver</ent>⟦br⟧
